high_descs: Head rotate and turn near the shelf.
Pick up the leftmost newspaper; the one in the shade.
Go back towards the door, then turn right and walk to the desklamp in the corner.
anns.task_desc: Examine a newspaper by the light of a DeskLamp.

high_descs: Turn around the right and turn left to the shelf.
Take a newspaper from the shelf.
Turn around the left, move forward, turn left and turn right to the desk lamp.
anns.task_desc: Take a newspaper from the shelf and turn on the desk lamp.

high_descs: Turn around and head straight, then proceed to turn left towards the shelf
Pick up newspaper from the shelf
Turn around and make a straight turn before proceeding to turn left towards the desk lamp
anns.task_desc: Examine a newspaper by the light of a desk lamp
